body.description: Clorox ToiletWand Disinfecting Refill Pack is preloaded with 4x the powerful cleaning action of Clorox Cleaner in every disposable cleaning head. The toilet wand system allows you to click a sponge like head onto the wand, scrub to unleash the preloaded cleaner, then toss the head away. These disposable cleaning heads kills germs, removes rust, calcium and lime scale while it disinfects, deodorizes and deep cleans with ease. Based on comparative lab tests, the toilet wand cleans better than a brush. The powerful disinfecting cleaning head is shaped so that you tackle every stain and every disgusting growth under the hard to reach areas of the bowl rim while killing 99.9% of germs like staphylococcus aureus, salmonella enterica, rhinovirus type 37 and influenza A. The Clorox ToiletWand Handle is sold separately. Just click your way to a cleaner toilet with the Clorox ToiletWand Disposable Toilet Cleaning System.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Hygiene Made Easy
reviews.reviewText: I've been using the Original Clorox ToiletWand Disinfecting Refills, scented with Rainforest Rush, in a 30-count pack, and they have transformed my bathroom cleaning routine. The convenience and value of these refills cannot be overstated. They attach easily to the ToiletWand handle, making the unpleasant task of scrubbing the toilet less of a chore and more of a quick, hygienic errand.Each disposable head is preloaded with Clorox cleaner, which gives me confidence in the disinfecting power I've come to expect from the Clorox brand. The Rainforest Rush scent leaves a fresh and clean aroma, which is a welcome departure from the harsh, chemical smell often associated with bathroom cleaners.The packaging may vary, but the effectiveness remains consistent. With 30 refills in one package, I am set for quite some time, which is not only convenient but also cost-effective. These refills, when used with the ToiletWand system, offer a sanitary solution by eliminating the need to store a germ-ridden toilet brush.For anyone looking to streamline their bathroom cleaning process while ensuring their toilet is left spotless and germ-free, the Clorox ToiletWand Disinfecting Refills are worth considering. They're a staple in my home, and I appreciate the cleanliness and ease they provide.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Who knew cleaning the toilet could be so fun??? Great value on refills.
reviews.reviewText: Say goodbye to the smelly old toilet brush that sits in the holder next to your toilet and say hello to the easiest way to keep your toilet fresh and clean without all the hassle of having the multiple steps of getting the toilet bowl cleaner, squirting it in the toilet, putting it away, getting out the toilet brush, cleaning the toilet, then having to rinse it off and put back in the little caddy where it drips water and sits until you use it again, and having to do that long process all over again, no wonder we dread cleaning the toilet. Make things simple and convenient and you will do it more often and dread it a little less. So yes, while it might seem a little more expensive or possibly wasteful to use and dispose of these little disinfecting refills, it will certainly clean your toilet amazingly, leave it smelling great, and with a touch of a button throw it out and put the handle away and you are done. I am not sure what magic they put in these little things, but they work like magic and can get some of the hardest water stains and buildup out (used at a friend's home who has really hard water build up and they had tried everything, brought this over and it was like magic and with a little elbow grease it was taking it off), and there is plenty of cleaner in one of these pads, I will usually be able to take a little disposable trash bag and carry the one I am using from one bathroom to the next and be able to clean both of my bathrooms with one, so it is less expensive and not wasteful. This was the best price I found online and certainly better than the grocery store. While I am still not a fan of cleaning the toilets, I can tell you this sure does help!! Great product, great quantity in this refill box, they are packaged in sleeves so you can place in multiple restrooms for storage until you need to use. Five stars, and a repeat customer.

No more dealing with dirty toilet brushes that breed bacteria and require endless cleaning and drying. With Clorox Toilet Wand Refills, simply snap on a fresh, pre-loaded head, clean to your heart's content, and dispose of it when finished—no mess, no fuss!I must also commend the thoughtful engineering of the Clorox Toilet Wand system. It's as if the designers at Clorox truly understand the importance of efficiency and simplicity in our cleaning routines.And let's not forget the refreshing scent! The subtle fragrance of each cleaning pad adds a delightful touch to the cleaning experience, leaving my bathroom smelling clean and inviting. It's a little dose of freshness that transforms the chore of toilet cleaning into a rejuvenating task.From a creative perspective, these Clorox Toilet Wand Refills have become an unexpected source of inspiration. I find myself in awe of their ability to transform the dull task of toilet cleaning into a moment of satisfaction and accomplishment. It's as if each swipe of the wand is a brushstroke, crafting a masterpiece of cleanliness and tranquility in my bathroom.In conclusion, Clorox Toilet Wand Disinfecting Refills are a true game-changer in the realm of toilet cleaning. Their unique design, powerful disinfecting properties, and hassle-free operation make them an indispensable tool in my cleaning arsenal. With Clorox Toilet Wand Refills, every visit to the bathroom becomes a delightful encounter with cleanliness and freshness.So, fellow cleanliness enthusiasts, let the Clorox Toilet Wand Refills be your trusty sidekick in the battle against bathroom grime. Embrace the ease, efficiency, and satisfaction they bring to your toilet cleaning routine. Prepare to bid farewell to scrub brushes and hello to a whole new level of cleanliness. Clorox Toilet Wand Refills—a remarkable cleaning companion that transforms your bathroom into a sanctuary of hygiene and beauty.
